Personal portfolio generated using my custom template generator.
(tem)plate, generator: https://github.com/x3hy/plate

For more information view my website here:
https://x3hy.github.io

.
├── generate.sh      | Use plate to load data to index.html
├── index.html       | The plate file (page with loaded data)
├── README           | This file
├── source           | Data source files
│   ├── entry.py     | Generate a new journal entry
│   ├── fetch.py     | Download the latest github api data
│   ├── journal.json | Data for journal entries
│   ├── repo.json    | Data for my repositories (from github api)
│   └── user.json    | Data for my user (from github api) 
├── source.html      | Original website code
└── src              | Website source files
    ├── date.js      | Generate "time-since" times from UTC dates
    ├── public.js    | Basic Javascript
    └── style.css    | Very few styles
                     |
---------------------'
